{"tid":427930,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"五毛運作原理，你問我答","createTime":"2017-10-07T16:57:28.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-14T15:35:10.000Z","uid":33307,"like":87,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"9a9bb13cf4a28dc3d3439fb87027a5722bbadea4","tid":427930,"uid":33307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T16:57:28.000Z","msg":"時事，新聞，政治係主戰場<br />\n<br />\n佢地首先會去其他版搞一輪出post<br />\n以防比人發現太明顯新註冊做打手<br />\n係香討就會去股票版出post/回廢post<br />\n連登高登就自然係波台<br />\n<br />\n之後玩法都係幾種<br />\n-唱淡反對派，降低對方士氣<br />\n-轉移焦點，出下風化post<br />\n-引起內訌，公屋私樓，港男港女，大學大專，泛民本土，其實好明顯<br />\n-洗版，令人睇唔到post討論<br />\n-玩膠，你認真佢就膠化你個post"},{"pid":"7be499a37071a64ff690e25cb943ad892d91ba39","tid":427930,"uid":105995,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T16:59:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6c24047e8769889864803aecbfd94b0ea7ca794","tid":427930,"uid":43189,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T17:10:27.000Z","msg":"有啲就出膠post起家先"},{"pid":"5f5a695c03c7c9c2ce3852011d7891dee0c05ed1","tid":427930,"uid":2436,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T17:26:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"eac9a555ff5753a6362e751d5d2d0b63336d8f08","tid":427930,"uid":48083,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T17:29:00.000Z","msg":"針對起底功能<br />\n<br />\n有啲係唔出post只係出reply+經常改名"},{"pid":"932cae3552ad40eec10fb00878db63e19823489a","tid":427930,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T17:29:12.000Z","msg":"針對起底功能<br />\n<br />\n有啲係唔出post只係出reply+經常改名"},{"pid":"a9277713e31fc4dcc1fc2dd8c04f456b69f755ab","tid":427930,"uid":53223,"like":0,"dislike":9,"score":-9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T17:30:28.000Z","msg":"階級矛盾本就是普遍存在於香港的"},{"pid":"a7c4bfdae6f67b352965da62791895d54be0b732","tid":427930,"uid":48083,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T17:33:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>階級